            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">Thailand Productivity Institute</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">Ministry of Industry</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <img src="https://www.foodfocusthailand.com/images/upload/10_Ratchanee.jpg" alt="Assoc. Prof.Ratchanee Kongkachuichai, Ph.D." />
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">Assoc. Prof.Ratchanee Kongkachuichai, Ph.D.</p>
